Water Level Detection: Uses multiple water level sensors to detect water levels at various percentages (25%, 50%, 70%, and 100%).
Wireless Communication: Transmits water level data via LoRa SX1278 module at 433 MHz, ensuring long-range communication.
Data Transmission Reliability: Implements error-checking mechanisms and retries to ensure reliable communication.
Dynamic Display: Displays water level and status information on a 1.8" TFT display.
ESP8266 and ESP32 Compatibility: Uses ESP8266 on the transmitter side and ESP32 on the receiver side.
Power-Saving Mode: Configured to reduce power consumption during idle periods.
